Package: visR
Type: Package
Title: A Package to Wrap Functionality for Plots, Tables and Diagrams Adhering to Graphical Principles
Description: The goal of 'visR' is to enable fit-for-purpose, reusable clinical and medical research focused visualizations and tables with sensible defaults and based on sound graphical principles.
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2021-06-02
